question.en: What is the ID of the claim that has the smallest amount of total settlement?

query.en: SELECT t1.Claim_ID FROM claims AS t1 JOIN settlements AS t2 ON t1.claim_id  =  t2.claim_id GROUP BY t1.claim_id ORDER BY sum(t2.settlement_amount) ASC LIMIT 1
query.pl: SELECT t1.Claim_ID FROM claims AS t1 JOIN settlements AS t2 ON t1.claim_id  =  t2.claim_id GROUP BY t1.claim_id ORDER BY sum(t2.settlement_amount) ASC LIMIT 1

question.en: Find the names of customers who have used both the service "Close a policy" or the service "Upgrade a policy".

query.en: SELECT t1.customer_name FROM customers AS t1 JOIN first_notification_of_loss AS t2 ON t1.customer_id  =  t2.customer_id JOIN services AS t3 ON t2.service_id  =  t3.service_id WHERE t3.service_name  =  "Close a policy" INTERSECT SELECT t1.customer_name FROM customers AS t1 JOIN first_notification_of_loss AS t2 ON t1.customer_id  =  t2.customer_id JOIN services AS t3 ON t2.service_id  =  t3.service_id WHERE t3.service_name  =  "Upgrade a policy"
query.pl: SELECT t1.customer_name FROM customers AS t1 JOIN first_notification_of_loss AS t2 ON t1.customer_id  =  t2.customer_id JOIN services AS t3 ON t2.service_id  =  t3.service_id WHERE t3.service_name  =  "Zamknij polisę" INTERSECT SELECT t1.customer_name FROM customers AS t1 JOIN first_notification_of_loss AS t2 ON t1.customer_id  =  t2.customer_id JOIN services AS t3 ON t2.service_id  =  t3.service_id WHERE t3.service_name  =  "Uaktualnij politykę"

question.en: Show me the id of organizations involved in less then 3000$ grant amount.

query.en: SELECT T2.organisation_id FROM Grants AS T1 JOIN Organisations AS T2 ON T1.organisation_id  =  T2.organisation_id GROUP BY T2.organisation_id HAVING sum(T1.grant_amount)  <  3000;
query.pl: SELECT T2.organisation_id FROM Grants AS T1 JOIN Organisations AS T2 ON T1.organisation_id  =  T2.organisation_id GROUP BY T2.organisation_id HAVING sum(T1.grant_amount)  <  3000;

query.en: SELECT T1.organisation_id FROM Organisations AS T1 JOIN Research_Staff AS T2 ON T1.organisation_id  =  T2.employer_organisation_id GROUP BY T1.organisation_id ORDER BY count(*) ASC LIMIT 1;
query.pl: SELECT T1.organisation_id FROM Organisations AS T1 JOIN Research_Staff AS T2 ON T1.organisation_id  =  T2.employer_organisation_id GROUP BY T1.organisation_id ORDER BY count(*) ASC LIMIT 1;

question.en: Which station ids never had more than 12 bikes available?

query.en: SELECT DISTINCT station_id from status where station_id not in (SELECT station_id from status where bikes_available > 12)
query.pl: SELECT DISTINCT station_id from status where station_id not in (SELECT station_id from status where bikes_available > 12)

question.en: Which zip code had at least 100 trips taking place there?
question.pl: Który kod pocztowy obejmował co najmniej 100 przejazdów?

query.en: SELECT DISTINCT zip_code FROM trip GROUP BY zip_code HAVING count(*)  >=  100
query.pl: SELECT DISTINCT zip_code FROM trip GROUP BY zip_code HAVING count(*)  >=  100

question.en: Which end station names have more than 100 trips ending there?
question.pl: Które nazwy stacji końcowych kończą się ponad 100 razy?

query.en: SELECT DISTINCT end_station_name FROM trip GROUP BY end_station_name HAVING count(*)  >  100
query.pl: SELECT DISTINCT end_station_name FROM trip GROUP BY end_station_name HAVING count(*)  >  100

question.en: How many trips started from Mountain View city
question.pl: Ile podróży rozpoczęło się z miasta Mountain View?

query.en: SELECT count(*) FROM station AS T1 JOIN trip AS T2 JOIN station AS T3 JOIN trip AS T4 ON T1.id  =  T2.start_station_id AND T2.id  =  T4.id AND T3.id  =  T4.end_station_id WHERE T1.city  =  "Mountain View"
query.pl: SELECT count(*) FROM station AS T1 JOIN trip AS T2 JOIN station AS T3 JOIN trip AS T4 ON T1.id  =  T2.start_station_id AND T2.id  =  T4.id AND T3.id  =  T4.end_station_id WHERE T1.city  =  "Widok z góry"
